snippet: Jae Crowder had 22 points, and the Boston Celtics extended their home win streak to 11 with a 100-95 victory over the Utah Jazz on Monday night....
lead_paragraph: Jae Crowder had 22 points, and the Boston Celtics extended their home win streak to 11 with a 100-95 victory over the Utah Jazz on Monday night.

headline.main: Celtics' Home Streak Reaches 11 With 100-95 Win Over Jazz
